data.description:
LOCATION IS IDEAL, less than 4 miles from the heart of downtown OS, and 2 miles from exit 50 of I10, and less than 10 miles to Keesler Air Force Base.
This home, built in December 2021, has been a second home, so it has been very gently used. Being sold WITH the new Fridge and washer and dryer and window treatments, it is now BETTER THAN NEW. No flood is required and the two year old home will have low insurance. 
The open floorpan  is great for entertaining as the ground floor is a huge great room, with an island in the spacious kitchen, and a half bath. Upstairs are three bedrooms, two baths and laundry, complete with a brand new washer & dryer.
This home is situated on one of a very few extra large lots, and has no homes behind it or one side, allowing for great privacy. Community pool and club house. Ask to see this one TODAY!
